data.title: Street Warrior (1987)
data.meta_description: Street Warrior: Directed by Willy Milan. With Alicia Alonzo, Anthony Alonzo, Raul Aragon, Vic Diaz. Owner of a small business in the market gets tired of being beaten by the leader of a street gang and kills him, becoming a popular hero himself. Afterwards, he finds out he's being manipulated and accused of political crimes. He plans a revenge.
